title: The Queen's Megaron (Palace of Minos)
description: The Queen's Megaron is a room in the Minoan "Palace of Minos" at Knossos. It includes the famous Dolphin fresco.

properties.description: The Queen's Megaron is a suite in the Minoan "Palace of Minos" at Knossos. It includes the famous Dolphin fresco, a bathroom, a toilet room, and a light well.
properties.title: The Queen's Megaron at Knossos
